WEBVTT

00:09:28.254 --> 00:09:30.952
that are all meant
to bring people together.

00:09:32.032 --> 00:09:35.309
Zachary Elementary School
in Zachary, Louisiana,

00:09:35.333 --> 00:09:37.881
has something they call
a "Midweek Meetup,"

00:09:37.905 --> 00:09:40.064
where they invite teachers to share lunch

00:09:40.088 --> 00:09:42.974
and to talk about the things
that are going well

00:09:42.998 --> 00:09:46.320
and the things that are weighing
heavy on their hearts.

00:09:47.553 --> 00:09:52.569
These schools are making space
for conversations that matter.

00:09:53.792 --> 00:09:56.601
Finally, my friend
and colleague Jen Highstreet

00:09:56.625 --> 00:09:58.768
takes five minutes out of each day

00:09:58.792 --> 00:10:01.331
to write an encouraging
note to a colleague,